      "content": "i don't even know why i'm typing this. everything just... it's all gone. the lab results, the funding, the last four years of my life. it's just gone. i feel like i'm just a hollow shell of a person and there's no way to fix it. i am just so incredibly tired of trying to fight for a life that doesn't even feel like mine anymore. i just want the noise to stop. i just want peace.",
